%% Diagram: Optimistic Update with Rollback
%% Type: sequenceDiagram
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as UI
    participant S as Local Store + Pending Queue
    participant Srv as Server

    U->>UI: click toggle
    UI->>S: snapshot previous, apply optimistic, enqueue mutation
    UI-->>U: render new state immediately
    UI->>Srv: PATCH /todos/:id (idempotency key)

    alt Success
        Srv-->>UI: 200 ack
        UI->>S: dequeue mutation, clear pending marker
    else Validation failure (4xx)
        Srv-->>UI: 422
        UI->>S: restore snapshot, drop mutation
        UI-->>U: show error
    else Network failure
        Srv -x UI: timeout
        UI->>S: keep mutation pending
        UI->>Srv: retry with backoff
        Note over UI,S: after persistent failure: rollback and surface to user
    end
